targets.rawSql:
SELECT
  date AS "time",
  fz_icu as "ICU Fallzahl",
  fz_icu_free + fz_icu as "ICU Kapazität",
  (fz_icu::float / (fz_icu_free + fz_icu)) * 100 as "ICU Auslastung %"
FROM fallzahlen
WHERE
  date BETWEEN '${__from:date:YYYY-MM-DD}' AND '${__to:date:YYYY-MM-DD}'
  AND bundesland = $bundesland
ORDER BY 1
